---

## 1. Directory Tree (excluding node_modules, .git)

There is no `node_modules` directory — the project has zero installed dependencies. The full tree:

```
workspace/
├── AGENTS.md
├── README.md
├── package.json
├── tests-before.log
├── data/
│   └── collections.json
├── migrations/
